{"tid":2193901,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習近平：重大危機面前沒任何一個國家可獨善其身","createTime":"2020-09-08T07:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T11:44:38.000Z","uid":241764,"like":37,"dislike":123,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"fbca08b560c6d65910130587bbfb9178fb75b176","tid":2193901,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:36:55.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平在全國抗擊新冠肺炎疫情表彰大會上發表講話，指出新冠肺炎疫情告誡世人，人類是榮辱與共的命運共同體，<span class=\"gold\">重大危機面前沒有任何一個國家可以獨善其身，任何自私自利、嫁禍他人、顛倒是非、混淆黑白的做法，不僅會對本國和本國人民造成傷害，而且會給世界各國人民帶來傷害。</span><br />\n<br />\n習近平說，中國將繼續推進疫情防控的國際合作，但同時表示中國要堅持底線思維、增強憂患意識，防範和化解各種風險，辯證認識和把握國內外大勢，加強戰略性、系統性、前瞻性的研究謀劃，做好較長時間應對外部環境變化的思想和工作準備，發揚鬥爭精神，敢於鬥爭、善於鬥爭，及時調整鬥爭策略，團結一切可以團結的力量，不斷奪取偉大鬥爭新勝利。<br />\n<br />\n全文: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548463-20200908.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548463-20200908.htm&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=50349697\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548463-20200908.htm&h=0891ae24\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548463-20200908.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n又想曲線話人屈佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e170d2ea65c3f53d71be59d657dc74c8793426","tid":2193901,"uid":155095,"like":100,"dislike":1,"score":99,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/84978891_2632550820187417_3689009769164570624_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=dZgjdL0dVokAX-R0RiC&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg6-1.fna&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=82c7c63db402c1e2f304a9250e7c8082&amp;oe=5F7D191D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F84978891_2632550820187417_3689009769164570624_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DdZgjdL0dVok