麼不聰明呀⋯⋯第二階段是正面衝突一敗塗地，但資源還沒有輸光的時候，表現為滿世界遊走，在你背後造謠說你多壞而不是多蠢⋯⋯第三階段是資源輸光，滾社會收穫無數涼薄，表現為一面苦苦哀求，同時突然魚死網破地攻擊，結果以沒有資源的無效掙扎，把斬草除根的借口送給你。中國機關家屬院見過了太多這樣的劇本，當事人雖然不是國際政治勢力，但人的本性和世界的劇本在哪都是一樣的。"},{"pid":"dfde4f733a98c2c241ccd2d18eeb37fc1e0076bf","tid":2193901,"uid":338439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:43:34.000Z","msg":"佢幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cfadecc5e13db16edc1cfd693e8a7e05e8d20f7","tid":2193901,"uid":522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:44:28.000Z","msg":"將病毒周圍散播就話唔可以獨善其身<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04eb324c9d2329d3ac7eb59569a28155601f4c32","tid":2193901,"uid":237465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:49:11.000Z","msg":"重大危機 ? 唔知係邊個撚樣輸出 呢 ?"},{"pid":"bda5847ec2a6177d83ff9f9af7578b53d55cca1a","tid":2193901,"uid":63543,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:49:45.000Z","msg":"重大<span class=\"red\">生化病毒武器</span>面前沒有國家可以獨善其身"},{"pid":"75f8c894181ac2d99c97ebc05583b2409e7714c6","tid":2193901,"uid":291526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:50:42.000Z","msg":"做咩成日鬧自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a822f19af5179a345b9c2d8f0ed94d35cf9256c","tid":2193901,"uid":332752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:50:45.000Z","msg":"支那咪係全世界個個既重大危機<br />\n佢意思係咪想更多國家加入圍毆支那系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72adffeed351dc72485d5784fa01afb03c68cba5","tid":2193901,"uid":38982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:50:56.000Z","msg":"係咪恐嚇緊其他國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a029ead948e5a421e4471af73298abfc5a848a0","tid":2193901,"uid":300644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1